	<h3 class="entry-title mh-posts-grid-title">
		<a href="https://www.thevoiceofchinese.com/%e6%9c%80%e6%96%b0%e6%96%b0%e9%97%bb/%e7%be%8e%e5%9b%bd%e8%bf%9e%e6%b1%9f%e5%85%ac%e4%bc%9a%e6%8b%9c%e8%ae%bf%e7%90%af%e5%a4%b4%e9%95%87%e4%be%a8%e8%81%94/" title="美国连江公会拜访琯头镇侨联" rel="bookmark">
			美国连江公会拜访琯头镇侨联		</a>
	</h3>
	<div class="mh-meta entry-meta">
<span class="entry-meta-date updated"><i class="fa fa-clock-o"></i><a href="https://www.thevoiceofchinese.com/2019/04/">04/04/2019</a></span>
</div>
	<div class="mh-posts-grid-excerpt clearfix">
		<div class="mh-excerpt"><p>【中国侨声网记者李兆银纽约报道】 4月4日、美國連江公會拜訪琯头鎮僑聯 <a class="mh-excerpt-more" href="https://www.thevoiceofchinese.com/%e6%9c%80%e6%96%b0%e6%96%b0%e9%97%bb/%e7%be%8e%e5%9b%bd%e8%bf%9e%e6%b1%9f%e5%85%ac%e4%bc%9a%e6%8b%9c%e8%ae%bf%e7%90%af%e5%a4%b4%e9%95%87%e4%be%a8%e8%81%94/" title="美国连江公会拜访琯头镇侨联">[&#8230;]</a></p>
</div>	</div>
</article></div>
</div>
</section>
